elements.text:
when entering a workspace for the second time:
---
* restoring workspace:
  - flow needs the nodes and edges list with all 
    the reactflow props for putting it back to its position

* restoring node state:
  - the node needs to restore the state value (string) of 
    the state machine and with that it can enter its cycle 
    (ie checking unfinished jobs and changing its state to 
    the aproppriate color)
